data.description: Welcome to this charming townhouse in the sought-after Southwind community on South Fulton Parkway. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, the airport, and more, the property boasts a desirable layout with the primary bedroom featuring an en-suite on the main floor. Additionally, enjoy a loft overlooking the two-story living room and two spacious bedrooms upstairs.    Luxury touches abound, including a newly installed custom carriage garage door, updated painted shutters, and a freshly painted front door. The interior boasts recent updates, including a new hot water tank and thermostat, with dual individual controls for upstairs and main level AC. Revel in the convenience of a gas starter decorative fireplace in the two-story living room.    Southwind offers a host of amenities, including a clubhouse, pool, tennis, and basketball courts on-site. This well-maintained, master-planned golf, swim, and tennis community is the epitome of comfort and convenience. With low annual HOA dues, this is an exceptional opportunity for thriving South Fulton County living.    Don't miss your chance to own the largest townhome plan in this community, featuring a multi-use loft area and three generously sized bedrooms with ample closet space. Embrace the lifestyle of Southwind—a place where luxury meets functionality.
